{"tid":2105764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三峽大壩上游四川阿壩州再發生4級極淺層地震","createTime":"2020-07-13T00:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T06:38:06.000Z","uid":184679,"like":322,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"314ca6b1eb97203851f2d09b79187f88ce4a8363","tid":2105764,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:59:59.000Z","msg":"中國整個長江流域正爆發1988年以來最大洪災，已經有高達27省市受災，中國逾半江山都泡在水中，災情還在持續，鄱陽湖水位已經爆漲到超越青海湖成為中國最大湖，同時，地震接踵而至，光昨（7月12日）中國4省市連發4個地震，其中唐山地震5.1級（美國地質調查所（USGS）公布為芮氏規模4.7），後又連續33次餘震，且三峽大壩上游的四川阿壩區再發生4級地震，再度引發對三峽大壩安全的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3226345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3226345&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=6742bc35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3226345&h=a296602f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3226345</a>"},{"pid":"92a6b0344885f913f29052cc6b01a93eaafd32d4","tid":2105764,"uid":121146,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:00:30.000Z","msg":"太少"},{"pid":"14995d7055e95ffa089946d890b6087deef97786","tid":2105764,"uid":259088,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaf416bf7808f372a865a640d2b3ebc9831dcb98","tid":2105764,"uid":253016,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"冇食飯 打尿震都大力過你"},{"pid":"3738fe16343d65af64aee5028f5db1cef376f972","tid":2105764,"uid":51701,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:01:53.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳可防可控"},{"pid":"e4716c145d79417d6e6f655b5280fb8c9925d81a","tid":2105764,"uid":281492,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:02:12.000Z","msg":"美斯兒美斯兒"},{"pid":"5af684e4f2c7ce4d8d3c350d2cf439b11d9ee527","tid":2105764,"uid":58841,"lik